Beyond the Gates of Bel Air…

10950 Bellagio Road | $17,998,000
Lower Bel Air Estates, Los Angeles
6 Beds | 6 Baths | 7,820 SF

Experience the pinnacle of prestige and privacy at this magnificent English Manor, set behind gates on a nearly one-acre lot with commanding views over the fairways of the Bel Air Country Club.

A stately motor court welcomes you to a world of refined living—where soaring vaulted ceilings, exposed beams, a grand fireplace, and oversized windows set the tone for unforgettable entertaining.

The chef’s kitchen is a designer’s dream, featuring a La Cornue range, custom cabinetry, and curated finishes throughout. Flowing seamlessly into the dining room and sun-drenched indoor/outdoor living areas, every corner of this estate is intentional and inspired.

Step through French doors to discover a private outdoor sanctuary: a 15-foot waterfall spilling into a tranquil pool, alfresco dining terraces, and secluded yoga decks—designed for both indulgence and serenity.

The primary suite rivals a luxury hotel, with a spa-like marble bath, a 2-level boutique closet, a private fireplace, and a secluded terrace with uninterrupted views.

10950 Bellagio is more than a home—it’s a legacy address.

This is where timeless architecture, privacy, and luxury converge in one of L.A.’s most iconic neighborhoods.
